
<div class="card text-white border-0 w-100">
    <div class="card-background">
        <div class="card-body mask mask-custom h-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-around">
            <div class="f-flex flex-column">
                <h1 class="card-title display-1 p-0">QualiTrackr</h1>
                <p class="card-text fs-2 px-3">
                    Make quality records a breeze with this all-in-one tool
                </p>

            </div>
            
            <div class="m-4">
                <%= video_tag "factory_loop.mp4", 
                    controls: true, 
                    autoplay: true, 
                    loop: true, 
                    muted: true, 
                    width: "600",
                    height: "315",
                    id: "video" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<div class="container my-3">
  <div id="info" class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <h4 class="my-3">Revolutionize Your PPAP Documentation Process</h5>
        <p>
            
            Struggling with the complexity of creating and managing PPAP documentation? 
            This innovative document management system consolidates all PPAP components 
            into one streamlined platform. Designed for the manufacturing industry, 
            fully customizable, this solution simplifies the Production 
            Part Approval Process, giving you a competitive edge by reducing delays and enhancing customer satisfaction. 
            Stay ahead of global sustainability regulations and ensure smooth, timely production with this all-in-one PPAP management tool.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
        <h4>Contact me:</h4>
        <form class="w-50">
            <div data-mdb-input-init class="form-outline mb-4">
                <input type="text" id="form4Example1" class="form-control" />
                <label class="form-label" for="form4Example1">Name</label>
            </div>

            <div data-mdb-input-init class="form-outline mb-4">
                <input type="email" id="form4Example2" class="form-control" />
                <label class="form-label" for="form4Example2">Email address</label>
            </div>

            <div data-mdb-input-init class="form-outline mb-4">
                <textarea class="form-control" id="form4Example3" rows="4"></textarea>
                <label class="form-label" for="form4Example3">Message</label>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <button data-mdb-ripple-init type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block w-50 mb-4">Send</button>
            </div>
            
        </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
